name: Anthill (itch) (Zelik_Mrakoroy, CyclopCamishok)
description:
Anthill (itch) (Zelik_Mrakoroy, CyclopCamishok) is a simulation game developed by Zelik_Mrakoroy and CyclopCamishok. It was originally released in 2023.
Anthill (itch) (Zelik_Mrakoroy, CyclopCamishok) is available on PC. The game is sold via itch.io.
